  "title": "Manicurist",
  "description": "<p>We are expanding and is looking for <strong>passionate & skilled Manicurists</strong> to join our growing team!</p><p>✨ <strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li><p>Manicure & pedicure services</p></li><li><p>Gel / classic nail polish application</p></li><li><p>Basic nail art (training provided if needed)</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness & hygiene of work area</p></li><li><p>Provide friendly and professional customer service</p></li></ul><p>✨ <strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Experience as a manicurist preferred (training can be provided for the right attitude)</p></li><li><p>Passion for nails & beauty</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude, responsible & team-oriented</p></li><li><p>Willing to learn and grow with the brand</p></li></ul><p>✨ <strong>What We Offer</strong></p><ul><li><p>Competitive salary + commission</p></li><li><p>Friendly & supportive work environment</p></li><li><p>Career growth opportunities</p></li><li><p>Training & skill upgrading</p></li><li><p>Staff perks & benefits</p></li></ul>",
